  <summary>8/5/2010--Introduced.
Recognizes the Cumbres &amp; Toltec Scenic Railroad (C&amp;TSRR) days. Acknowledges the critical role of freight and passenger rail in our nation's intermodal transportation system. Commends efforts of the state governments of Colorado and New Mexico, the C&amp;TSRR Commission, the C&amp;TSRR Management Company, and Friends of the C&amp;TSRR for their efforts to maintain this historic and scenic railroad.</summary>
